node.text:
We were fortunate enough to spend a weekend in Yokosuka, Japan entertaining the families living on the base there. We would like to thank the staff of the HMS Albion for their wonderful tour. 
Featuring Dakota Roche, Gary Young, Matthias Dandois, Josh Borden and Omar Hassan.

Video: Colin Mackay

node.text: Jason Watts (@wattzup) is back in USA! We haven’t seen him since March 2020. He’s two from our last photo shoot together pre COVID with @JeffZPhoto. Jason plans on being here a while so look for the @FastAndLooseBMX crew to turn it up with another member back mixing it with the squad.

Look for many of the Vans crew out there including @CalvinKosovich @JulianMolina_BMX @GGuendulain @BrunoHoffmann @Alex_Donnachie @AnthonyPerrin__ and of course, Courage. Clip courtesy of 🎥 @Rafael.Black
